  "helpFaqSectionTitle": "Frequently Asked Questions",
  "helpFaqEmpty": "No topic matches your search.",
  "helpFaqQ1": "How do I create a class?",
  "helpFaqA1": "To create a class, go to the \"My Classes\" tab in the main menu. Tap the \"+\" button at the top right, give the class a name, and tap \"Save\". An invite code is generated automatically when the class is created.",
  "helpFaqQ2": "How do I invite students?",
  "helpFaqA2": "Open the detail of the class you created. Share the class's invite code with your students; the student is added to your class by entering this code on the \"Join a Class\" screen in the app.",
  "helpFaqQ3": "How do I add words to a lesson (OCR + manual)?",
  "helpFaqA3": "Start the \"Add Words\" flow in the lesson detail. With manual entry, you type the English term and its Turkish meaning. For OCR, you write the words on paper and scan them with the camera or gallery; you review and edit the recognized words, then save them.",
  "helpFaqQ4": "How do I create and assign a puzzle?",
  "helpFaqA4": "After preparing your word list, open the \"Create New Puzzle\" flow, choose the game type and word list, then pick the classes that will solve the puzzle and publish it. The puzzle is assigned as homework to active students.",
  "helpFaqQ5": "Where do I see student results?",
  "helpFaqA5": "You can see shared results from the \"Reports\" tab or from the relevant student's detail. Each result shows the completion time and accuracy rate.",
  "helpFaqQ6": "I forgot my password, what should I do?",
  "helpFaqA6": "Tap the \"Forgot Password\" link on the login screen and enter your registered email address. Follow the instructions sent to you to set a new password.",
  "helpContactTitle": "Still need help?",
  "helpContactDesc": "Our team is here to answer your questions. Reach out to us anytime.",
